@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nfynad(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 + ((v1 + 0.33 - tmp + 0.25) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.24)))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v0 + 0.61) - (v1 + 0.56 + tmp + 0.44)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.32 - tmp + 0.84)) / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
